\"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom_Derby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epsom_Derby\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998382110434496, \"rank\": 0.0001530742507469279, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadija_bint_Khuwaylid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khadija\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadija_bint_Khuwaylid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadija_bint_Khuwaylid\"}, {\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 3.856490087765109e-12, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it means Lewis Richardson must beat Serbia's Vakhid Abbasov in his opening 71kg showdown later on Wednesday in order to avoid the ignominy of the squad returning home without a win to their name.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\", \"score\": 0.9965136461602875, \"rank\": 0.0034965034965035347, \"text\": \"Lewis Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6505700454618455, \"rank\": 0.5368840571666466, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like team-mates Rosie Eccles andDelicious Orie, Reid also found herself on the end of a contentious verdict against a vastly experienced opponent who is the current IBA world heavyweight champion.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"score\": 0.8664085269677004, \"rank\": 0.1516750654885949, \"text\": \"Rosie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosie_M._Banks\"}, {\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"score\": 0.9999971448676037, \"rank\": 2.1760876878617312e-06, \"text\": \"Eccles\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\"}, {\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9285079603244342, \"rank\": 0.07676929253311655, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reid boxed superbly from the centre of the ring to take the opening round all five judges' cards before Mardi fought back to effectively level going into the last.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was always going to be a tall order for Reid to come out on top in a final three-minute showdown but she arguably landed the cleaner work through her taller opponent's guard and could count herself unfortunate to drop the verdict.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless it was a performance to be proud of by Reid, a former celebrated junior who only returned to the sport in April last year after six years out due to degenerative disc disease.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reid cut a philosophical figure in the mixed zone, refusing to blame bad luck for a series of decisions that privately GB chiefs believe ought not to have gone against them.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\", \"score\": 0.5048875459231532, \"rank\": 0.7493148486484867, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gigabyte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I definitely won the first round but then she changed her tactics and made it a bit harder.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried to stick to my plan but unfortunately she got the decision,\\\" said Reid.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel so blessed just to have qualified and boxed the rest in the world.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whatever happens now I am an Olympian.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2133, \"end\": 2141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999947544619108, \"rank\": 5.245394700769492e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's something that cannot be taken off me and it'll stick with me for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel so blessed to have been part of this team, just to be here with the best team and support staff.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have all been sticking together and supporting each other.\\\"\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britainsent two boxers to the Atlanta Olympics in 1996 - David Burke and Fola Okesola - and both were beaten in their opening bouts.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1009331102289167e-15, \"text\": \"Atlanta Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2468, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Burke_(British_actor)\", \"score\": 0.6045936007865396, \"rank\": 0.3789915966386611, \"text\": \"David Burke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Burke_(British_actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Burke_(British_actor)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": []}]}"